<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>jobCrawler</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
    <link href="css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/carousel.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="css/index.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
                <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">jobCrawler</a>
        </div>
        <div id="navbar" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                <li><a href="/">主页</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">关于</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">联系我们</a></li>
                <li><a href="/search">搜索</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
    </div>
</nav>
<!-- Carousel
================================================== -->
<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <!-- Indicators -->
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item active">
            <img class="first-slide" src="images/10.png" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>爬虫搜集</h1>
                    <p>基于Node爬虫技术，轻量高效。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img class="second-slide" src="images/11.png" alt="Second slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>按需查找</h1>
                    <p>按条件寻找你需要的就业信息</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img class="third-slide" src="images/12.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>后台数据管理</h1>
                    <p>后台可以查看所爬取的就业信息，并可以删除过时的信息。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div><!-- /.carousel -->
<!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
================================================== -->
<!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->
<div class="container marketing">
    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4" id="about">
            <img class="img-circle" src="images/about.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>关于我们</h2>
            <p>该系统主要利用爬虫技术，从各大就业招聘信息的网站爬取数据，并存储在数据库中，可以实现实时爬取数据，保证数据库为实时数据库。最后将就业信息高效、快速、方便地呈现给用户看。</p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4" id="contact">
            <img class="img-circle" src="images/contact.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>联系我们</h2>
            <p>联系人：廖泽杰</p>
            <p>邮箱：1035123023@qq.com</p>
            <p>电话：15521075016</p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img class="img-circle" src="images/search.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image" width="140" height="140">
            <h2>搜索</h2>
            <p>从这里开始你的搜索之旅吧，点击下方按钮即可进入搜索页面，按条件查找你需要的就业信息。</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/search" role="button">开始搜索 &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div><!-- /.row -->
</div>
<!-- footer -->
<footer class="footer">
    <p>CopyRight&copy;Jonen,2018</p>
</footer>
<script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
